.PP
\fB\fCspan\-review\fR [\fB\fC\-server\fR \fIurl\fP] [\fB\fC\-span\-config\fR \fIfile\fP] [\fB\fC\-c\fR \fIfile\fP] [\fB\fC\-a\fR] [\fB\fC\-t\fR] [\fB\fC\-ticket\fR \fInumber\fP]
